java.io.Serializable
public class SKMapsInitializationException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException

Thrown to indicate that the application has attempted to use the SKMaps library without initializing it. SKMaps library is initialized by calling SKMaps.initializeSKMaps(android.content.Context, SKMapsInitSettings) .

2.5
